<p>&nbsp;The company’s customer service standards go beyond simply offering vehicles. Empire Rent A Car provides affordable pricing, frequent discounts, new and well-maintained vehicles, and unlimited mileage plans on local passenger van rentals. Many vehicles come with unrestricted travel options, allowing for cross-country trips. The company also offers flexible payment methods for added convenience. Renting from Empire means interacting with real people rather than automated systems, ensuring a personalized and responsive experience from the initial call to the return of the vehicle.</p>
<p>&nbsp;Despite its growth, Empire Rent A Car remains a family-owned business that values genuine connections with its customers. The company strives to combine the affordability and wide selection of large chains with the flexibility, attention, and one-on-one support that only a locally owned business can offer. Customer reviews consistently reflect this commitment to service and reliability. With more than 50 years of experience, Empire Rent A Car continues to be a trusted name for passenger vans, sprinter vans, minivans, delivery vans, cargo vans, production vans, economy cars, midsize cars, TLC cars, midsize SUVs, large SUVs, pickup trucks, moving trucks, box trucks, and refrigerated box trucks. The company remains dedicated to its mission of making the rental process simple and customer-focused for every traveler.</p>
